{"tid":1539653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望何君堯帶頭叫議員反對「撤回」動議","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:14:58.000Z","uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5748c626f6b5e6f3880a84c541490f8655bdc482","tid":1539653,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb29d5b98c1016cfb32f2536efa8743cf3f6beff","tid":1539653,"uid":219835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"支持何律師同奶共黨堅決擁護並通過逃犯條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a911884a820565ed374eda7355cea973a7db22d","tid":1539653,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d9a8ef5b345d52f3e7a7d9f222ac28d9e486cb","tid":1539653,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ap2yDcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih